    "description": "It's getting late for the citizens of Bedtime Town, and it looks like there's one peculiar fellow who's up way past his bedtime...<br><br>Mr. Sleepy Man is a sandbox-adventure where you play as a sleepy guy who's not really in control of his own actions. It's up to you to decide whether this world is a sweet dream or a nightmare. <br><br>Mr. Sleepy Man has many tricks up his...pajamas. He can just about interact with anything he gets his little hands on. Let's hope he doesn't accidently break someone's dreams in the process.<br><br><strong>What can Mr. Sleepy Man do? </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> He can pick up almost anything he finds,</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/fc28bae7ae57d490a68a15743263f593.poster.avif?t=1724476693\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/fc28bae7ae57d490a68a15743263f593.webm?t=1724476693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/fc28bae7ae57d490a68a15743263f593.mp4?t=1724476693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> jump his way through countless obstacles,</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/08b6e62d488d0536677cc7df6594d89b.poster.avif?t=1724476693\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/08b6e62d488d0536677cc7df6594d89b.webm?t=1724476693\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1888730/extras/08b6e62d488d0536677cc7df6594d89b.mp4?t=1724476693\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video